{"tid":1737991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我話嘅，呢場運動會輸喺香港人唔三罷","createTime":"2019-11-19T06:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T07:42:41.000Z","uid":240250,"like":39,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e1694127cc323f233039b14eb208921c008e077b","tid":1737991,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:06:23.000Z","msg":"反修例運動至今已經打左五個幾月，示威活動慢慢由爭取五大訴求變成警民衝突，結果係點大家都知啦，就係武鬥輸鳩梗，前線手足被捕、死傷，已經所剩無幾。<br />\n<br />\n但係邊個令到事情變到咁惡劣呢？係黑警？林鄭？習近平？都唔係，而係大部分香港人嘅選擇，佢地選擇袖手旁觀，明明三罷係對準政權，但佢地唔做，寧願享受手足們用血換取返嚟嘅「被罷工時間」。點解呢？因為大部分香港人都認為只要獨善其身，事情過後就可以過返以往嘅正常生活，想留條後路畀自己。<br />\n<br />\n搞成咁其實冇得點贏，一係投降，一係焦土，連班袖手旁觀嘅香港人都一次過燒埋。"},{"pid":"9b1792e39ba0b2b7bf335c46f51acd769e43c7f2","tid":1737991,"uid":240250,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"無差別裝修，無差別攻擊返工人士，真焦土"},{"pid":"58ce82c60b66462d59d7e8a1a465611090758568","tid":1737991,"uid":75655,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"放棄啦，已經輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c264e86ecce85888e612d4c90e16d0542232d49","tid":1737991,"uid":172893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"fd9e2f357aeee81f508b3a37c25ddf27f30dc3b0","tid":1737991,"uid":293368,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58ce82c60b66462d59d7e8a1a465611090758568","tid":1737991,"uid":75655,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"放棄啦，已經輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"收皮 你好煩"},{"pid":"c4a5f7c5267ba2b898c14cda595af8b26dd5f233","tid":1737991,"uid":210845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"輸你老母"},{"pid":"019b8fee01dc2fe23eabc2860e6bea18f383372d","tid":1737991,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:13:42.